onal bloggers with prominent social links in the header.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Take your favorite for a spin today!</p>\n<p><a href="https://revelardemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6690" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/revelar-ss-2/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630" data-orig-size="720,540" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=300" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=720" class="imgborder alignnone wp-image-6690" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630" alt="Revelar screenshot" width="840" height="630" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=300&amp;h=225 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://colsdemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6691" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/cols-ss-2/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=630" data-orig-size="880,660" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&