http://choycedesign.com">Mel Choyce</a> and developed by <a href="http://carolinemoore.net/">Caroline Moore</a>, Escutcheon &#8212; an unusual word referring to a <a href="http://finalfantasy.wikia.com/wiki/Escutcheon">type of shield</a> &#8212; supports a social icon menu and displays post excerpts on the front page.</p>\n<p><a href="http://escutcheondemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6602" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/07/05/escutcheon-toujours/escutcheon-ss/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=652" data-orig-size="1350,1048" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=652?w=300" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=652?w=840" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6602" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=652" alt="Escutcheon screenshot" width="840" height="652" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=840&amp;h=652 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=150&amp;h=116 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=300&amp;h=233 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=768&amp;h=596 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png?w=1024&amp;h=795 1024w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/escutcheon-ss.png 1350w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://twitter.com/laurelfulford">Laurel Fulford</a> crafted<a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/toujours/"><strong> Toujours</strong></a> (French for &#8220;always&#8221; &#8212; pronounced <em>too-DJOOR</em>) as a responsive remake of the popular Forever theme. Geared to weddings, it features a large slider (available via <a href="https://jetpack.com/">Jetpack</a> Featured Content), a unique layout for three recent posts, and a special <a href="https://toujoursdemo.wordpress.com/guestbook/">guestbook</a> template.</p>\n<p><a href="http://toujoursdemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6603" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/07/05/escutcheon-toujours/toujours-ss/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=679" data-orig-size="1358,1097" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=679?w=300" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=679?w=840" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6603" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=679" alt="Toujours screenshot" width="840" height="679" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=840&amp;h=679 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/toujours-ss.png?w=150&amp;h=121 1